{"tid":2106753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：民主派初選或構成国安法中顛覆政權罪行","createTime":"2020-07-13T13:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T01:32:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e10c6e8d6f918c76e1b98f340c89af75f8cd8b27","tid":2106753,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:13:30.000Z","msg":"民主派過去兩日舉行立法會選舉初選，有61萬人投票。行政長官林鄭月娥晚上回應指，大家有權投票，但選舉必須公平公正，不容許任何做法干擾立法會選舉，而香港選舉制度沒有初選機制。她說，政府不同部門收到相當多關於過去兩日活動的投訴，包括導致未來選舉不公平情況，亦涉嫌違反現時最多50人的限聚令，亦可能違反私隱保障，政府部門會調查，若有證據會行動。她又警告，所謂初選的目的，如果是達致35+選舉結果，目標去阻撓政府的政策，可能落入違反港區國安法中顛覆政權罪行，如果是這種情況就需要去處理。 <br />\n<br />\n她又說，過去兩日多人聚集，一旦因此出現新型冠狀病毒爆發，是遺憾的事。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346885&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=8bf76ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346885</a>"},{"pid":"e4a28748e71c009af8f7013baec507df75d40a59","tid":2106753,"uid":213628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034b028f0d60bfaaafe4968d395bb2fd6abe9abe","tid":2106753,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"拉曬60萬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c0091dec6312b5f96b73ce678b508aadb42084","tid":2106753,"uid":275218,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"又想助攻？"},{"pid":"64dcec0477601d082e295d46e81a42c56b987152","tid":2106753,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:14:41.000Z","msg":"如果是達致35+選舉結果，目標去阻撓政府的政策<br />\n<br />\n又改標題"},{"pid":"26a55db84e6525c1bf122dcd595c42fbcdf616c5","tid":2106753,"uid":301666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"